&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/EUR-LONDON-ALAIN-DUCASSE-DORCHESTER-OFFER-LOGO2.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7617&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/EUR-LONDON-ALAIN-DUCASSE-DORCHESTER-OFFER-LOGO2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;EUR- LONDON- ALAIN DUCASSE DORCHESTER- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;198&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;On the corner of Hyde Park in the lovely area of Mayfair, Alain Ducasse at The Dorchester is one of the most highly acclaimed restaurants in the United Kingdom &amp;#8211; one in only two restaurants to be holding 3 Michelin Stars in London. Gracious and attentive staff welcome guests into an elegant dining room decorated in a natural palette of tan, cream and taupe with unique touches at every turn. Alain Ducasse and Executive Chef Jocelyn Herland show their dedication to culinary arts in their cuisine, with signature dishes including&nbsp;&lsquo;Saut&eacute; gourmand&rsquo; of LOBSTER chicken quenelles and homemade pasta; and Simmered HALIBUT, winkles, cockles and razor clams &lsquo;marini&egrave;re&rsquo;.&nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;Please note that the attire is smart-elegant; jackets and collared shirts are preferred for gentlemen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Alain Ducasse at The Dorchester via phone +44-207-629-8866&nbsp;or via email&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:alainducassereservations@alainducasse-dorchester.com&quot;&gt;alainducassereservations@alainducasse-dorchester.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 72 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed 72 hour prior, the restaurant will reach out via phone or email. If reconfirmation contact is not made, the management reserves the right to release your booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

